ORG 0000H
LJMP main

ORG 0030H
DELAY : 
            MOV R1,#4
	  LOOP3: MOV R2,#250
	  LOOP2: MOV R3,#250
	  LOOP1: NOP
	  DJNZ R3,LOOP1
	  DJNZ R2,LOOP2
	  DJNZ R1,LOOP3
	  RET
	  
	  
ORG 0200H
main : MOV P1,#00H
repeat:    SETB P1.0
	   LCALL DELAY
	   CLR P1.0
	   LCALL DELAY 
	   LJMP repeat
	   
END 
